Package: libmrcam0
Section: libs
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Simple camera interface for genicam cameras
 Aravis provides a generic interface to genicam cameras. mrcam is a layer on top
 of aravis to provide simpler interfaces and tools for common use cases.
 .
 This package provides the runtime C libraries

